strings:
<voice_0x01001772><se_def>*: Well, it doesn't matter.
We're dying out anyway.

<voice_0x01001773><se_low>Chen Mui: Tell me! What is going on?
What in the world happened here?

<voice_0x01001774><se_def>*: Ah, Master Chen Mui.
I see you have returned to us.

<voice_0x01001775><se_def>*: You have my sympathies.
You've arrived just in time to witness
the end of the Dragovian race.

<voice_0x01001776><se_low>Chen Mui: The end of the Dragovians?
Things are even worse than they appear.

<voice_0x01001777><se_low>Chen Mui: We had better visit the other Elders.
We must get to the bottom of this!
